OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother bright day with some
OL,6,Fsunshine at times though high cloud
OL,7,Fwill turn this hazy. Becoming hot away
OL,8,Ffrom sea breezes, especially in the
OL,9,Fsouthwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry, but the chance of
OL,12,Fthe odd shower possible. Some
OL,13,Fbrightness at first, but widespread
OL,14,Flow cloud feeding in from the east
OL,15,Fthrough the evening, staying clearer
OL,16,Fin Southwest.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FA cooler and dull and cloudy
OL,19,Fday in the east, some limited
OL,20,Fbrightness possible in the afternoon.
OL,21,FBright, sunny and warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
